headline: Keysight and Point2 Technology Collaborate to Advance Next-Generation AI Scale-Up Interconnects
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., January 29, 2026--Collaboration validates Point2 Technology’s innovative e-Tube™ multi-terabit interconnects using Keysight's high-speed digital test solutions.
